{"type": "article", "id": 10443, "title": "向公众发售的军事坦克", "description": "", "date": "2015-06-05T07:14:45Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 26, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235936UitIVdpagbZQ4Pyr.png", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">这是把人惊呆的一个大家伙。最近，Ripsaw 推出了一款面向公众发售的军事坦克，可谓豪华震撼。不过它可不是用来打架的，这个坦克以 Ripsaw MS1 双轨机动车为原型，柴油引擎功率到达 600 马力。不仅如此，其舱内配备了丰富的娱乐设备。<a href=\"http://www.ripsawtank.com/ripsaw-ev2-media.html\" target=\"_blank\">这是 Ripsaw 官网</a>，感兴趣的话，不妨进去看看详细信息。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235933jX4FnA6eSpgI3JfC.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.68703704\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235933yBKA6SC9tahJXiPz.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66203704\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235934pdKVQz5ULGvNhX6J.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66203704\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235934KzciouZJVF8qXr6I.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66203704\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235935fe8gFIZXlj1P75DU.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66203704\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"><br>\r\n</span>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}